## Microsoft Entra ID Protection

[Try for free](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=2238349&clcid=0x409&culture=en-us&country=us)

[See plans and pricing](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/business/microsoft-entra-pricing)

 

**Microsoft Entra ID Protection is available with a subscription to Microsoft Entra ID P2 or Microsoft 365 E5:**

- Microsoft 365 E5 includes a free 30-day trial of Microsoft Entra ID P2 (Azure Active Directory P2).

- Azure and Office 365 subscribers can buy Microsoft Entra ID P2 online.